What you need to know:

Former Vice president Kalonzo Musyoka, Kenya Rugby Union chairman, Oduor Gangla, his predecessors Mwangi Muthee and Richard Omwela and officials from clubs that Ayimba played for were among those who paid their glowing tribute to the legend.Also to eulogise Ayimba was the Kenya Rugby League Federation chairman Richard Nyakwaka and Arigi Obiero on behalf of fans.